{"tid":94492,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)侏羅紀世界 最高危機 空軍一號","createTime":"2017-01-25T08:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T14:21:21.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c69e9563fb3639ab4f9b1164ee01c9e507eb4d5","tid":94492,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:59:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=mQqeVqlEYiUSzyOj6Sf6K3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=1c05b5db\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=mQqeVqlEYiUSzyOj6Sf6K3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=8a3af842\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/66/JurassicWorldComicConPoster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F66%2FJurassicWorldComicConPoster.jpg&h=f80c4ca2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/83/ExecutiveDecision_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F83%2FExecutiveDecision_poster.jpg&h=3f3df4c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b4/Air_force_one.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb4%2FAir_force_one.jpg&h=e3aca868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.侏羅紀公園事件22年後，努布拉島（中美洲離岸海島）成為了一個嶄新、名為「侏羅紀世界」的恐龍主題遊樂園。格雷&middot;米契爾與柴克&middot;米契爾兩兄弟前往該島探訪他們的阿姨兼樂園的營運經理&mdash;&mdash;克萊兒&middot;戴寧。她正忙於招攬新的贊助者。樂園即將登場的新賣點是一隻名為「帝王暴龍」的基因混合恐龍，牠體內有多種肉食恐龍及現代動物的基因，由遺傳學家吳亨利博士帶領的團隊製造<br />\n<br />\n2.一架載滿400名乘客的波音747從希臘雅典起飛前往美國華盛頓首府的途中，被一群由阿拉伯人納吉&middot;哈森帶領的恐怖份子挾持，要求美國釋放他們的首腦艾爾&middot;沙耶&middot;亞法，否則將在華盛頓上空引爆機上的毒氣彈，摧毀美國東岸超過四千萬條人命..<br />\n<br />\n3.在一場美俄特種部隊聯合的行動中，哈薩克共和國獨裁領袖芮狄被逮捕了。三週後，美國總統馬歇爾在俄羅斯國宴上發表了「絕不寬容」的演說，向全世界的恐怖份子表達立場。之後馬歇爾登上專機空軍一號由莫斯科起飛，沒想到有一群芮狄的支持者假扮成記者潛入了空軍一號上，並在起飛後因為一名總統特勤內奸的協助從而取得特勤局武器，在機上展開槍戰。儘管機組人員試圖在美軍駐德國的拉姆施泰因空軍基地緊急降落，但卻被劫機者殺死，挾持空軍一號重新起飛前往哈薩克..<br />\n<br />\n4 50PM左右播了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd002395f5fbbfe82071509382078a5595a9d94","tid":94492,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065e904a39ad2989cf213b7047c3edb421feddeb","tid":94492,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ff054cdf734df17017cd624072dd083077336a","tid":94492,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a34c16931c2fda55f20d07bf872fc99f9a5eff","tid":94492,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b0960d2443f5c87f1866deef0d36dadb0daacb","tid":94492,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\